                           Kostsyushko-Valyuzhinich (НА НЗХТ, д. 16, № 314; д. 36, л. 5, № 314).</rs>
                        <rs type="context">Southeast sector of the citadel of Chersonesos, Roman "citadel" (removed from the "additional" monastery wall constructed ca. 
                           1880 over the damaged sections of the ancient fortification wall).</rs>
                     </seg>
